dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Sauk_Zoning_2018.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Sauk_Airport_2018', 'Sauk_General_2018', and 'Sauk_Shoreland_2018'. [This feature class is used to maintain and display the current zoning information in the Sauk County GIS. Zoning Districts are administered by Sauk County for all Towns except the Town of Fairfield, Town of Delton, Town of Merrimac, and the Town of Washington.]
